Package Data

Interface Moveable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Entity
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Joueur

    public interface Moveable
extends Entity
    A class that implement the Data.Moveable interface is a piece on the board, able to move in a given direction ({Up, Down, Left, Right} axis). The speed at of the element can be set.
